text: Alive (, lit: A-live) is a 2020 South Korean zombie apocalypse action thriller movie, directed by Cho Il-hyung and starring: Yoo Ah-in, Park Shin-hye, Lee Hyun-woo, Lee Chae-kyung and Jeon Bae-soo. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2020 action movies Category:2020 thriller movies Category:2020s action thriller movies Category:South Korean movies Category:Korean-language movies Category:Zombie movies Category:Apocalyptic movies Category:Movies set in South Korea
